13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1085.66 of Title 82, unless
16 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17 A. 1. The Oklahoma Water Resources Board shall establish an
18 Oklahoma Water Infrastructure Loan Program. The program shall be
19 utilized to:
20 a. finance the development of water infrastructure
21 improvements through low-interest loans and grants to
22 municipalities, rural water districts, and other
23 eligible entities for approved water infrastructure
24 projects, and
SENATE FLOOR VERSION - SB265 SFLR Page 1
